		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)">Office of <persName>ALLEN &#38; CO.</persName>&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>6 BROAD STEET</placeName>&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>Decr. 18 1867</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir and friend</p>
				<p>Please send per express to<lb/> <persName>J. E. P. Lazarus</persName> <placeName>24 West 39th St</placeName>&#44;<lb/> 1 <sic>sett</sic> prayer books for which I<lb/> enclose check &#36;25.50 for the Books<lb/> and freight. I have not been<lb/> able to see any friend as yet in<lb/> regard to the Books.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Hoping you are feeling better</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I am yours very truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">M. M. Allen</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><placeName>P.O. Box 2380</placeName></p>
				<p><persName>Rev. I. I. Lyon</persName> says he can sell some<lb/> of your Books and wants 20&#37; discount<lb/> same as other agents. Do you agree&#63;<lb/> <persName role="author">M.</persName></p>
